dataIdInfo.idAbs:
Boundary delineation for all catchment high schools within the School District of Philadelphia. 'Neighborhood' schools utilize these boundaries to determine where students will be assigned. Special admission schools, which use different admission criteria, are excluded from this file.

Key Attribute Fields:

HS_ID : Catchment high school ID.

HS_Name : Catchment high school name.

HS_Short : Catchment high school abbreviated name.

HS_Gr : Catchment high school grade range.

HS_Level: Catchment high school level.
